Head. Ratio body length to antennae length up to 1.09. Number of eyes unclear, apparently 6, but all cornea reduced and actual number difficult to determine in most specimens; under light microscope eye number appears to vary from 3 to 6, whereas the single individual evaluated using SEM clearly shows 6 eyes (
Fig. 4
). Head dorsally (
